Neatline Maps requires Geoserver in order to function. Here's how to get a basic version of Geoserver up and running on your server:

- Download the Stable Binary(OS independent) Geoserver from Geoserver (http://geoserver.org/display/GEOS/Stable)
- Unzip the file
- From a terminal/command prompt, change into the geoserver directory
- Start Geoserver with java -jar start.jar
- Take a look at http://localhost:8080